        "content": "Candyfinity has a fluid rotation mechanism without any hesitations, thanks to HTML5 technology, which also allows gameplay on mobile devices. The basic layout consists of 6 reels and 3 rows with 729 ways to win, although these numbers are destined to increase during the Bonus game. The minimum bet is €0.20, but for an additional €0.10, the Golden Bet can be activated, increasing the chances of getting Bonus symbols. With the Autoplay function, you can choose to set between 10 and 1,000 automatic spins, although the game offers the possibility to have them go infinitely. If you opt for this solution, it is better to set the winning and losing limits that will stop the game once exceeded. Candyfinity has medium volatility and an RTP of 96%."
