    "content": "<p>What's better than hitting the jackpot? Unfortunately, Candyfinity doesn't come equipped with the traditional jackpot feature. But fear not my fellow sweet-toothed spinners! The game's medium volatility paves the way for some truly sweet payouts.</p><p>With a maximum payout of 20,000x the bet, you'll be able to enjoy your candy for weeks on end. Plus, think of all the dental bills you can pay off with that kind of cash. If you're anything like me, you'll just spend it all on more candy! </p>"
}

